        {
            "name": "Changeling Exile",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "This changeling exile is the child of a night hag or dreamthief hag.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Humanoid</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"14\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Society</a></u>)</b>: DC 18",
